      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i noticed something really weird with my smart thermostat and my fridge. everytime i get really worked up or stressed out late at night, the temp in the house drops like 3 degrees and the fridge starts making this loud humming noise. it's almost like they react to me. is there some kind of sensor link between them or something?",
